  "detailed_description": "<h1>FIND HMUR!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/467370/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.poster.avif?t=1764928114\" width=1170 height=426 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/467370/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.webm?t=1764928114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/467370/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.mp4?t=1764928114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/467370/extras/8eee270c063aadf8fe042814e72f4895.avif?t=1764928114\" width=400 height=100 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Escape This</strong></h2> is a casual puzzle game where the main objective is for the player to complete the given stage. <br>Each stage is selected at random.<br><br>All maps can be edited and you are also able to create your own unique maps and share them with the rest of the community.<br><br><strong>Can you escape?</strong>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/467370/extras/8eee270c063aadf8fe042814e72f4895.avif?t=1764928114\" width=400 height=100 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Escape This</strong></h2> is a casual puzzle game where the main objective is for the player to complete the given stage. <br>Each stage is selected at random.<br><br>All maps can be edited and you are also able to create your own unique maps and share them with the rest of the community.<br><br><strong>Can you escape?</strong>",
